{
  "stem": "3150.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So ?] [? he ?] [? talked ?] [? us ?] [? in, ?] [? to ?] [? get ?] [? coal. ?] And also, about a mile away from us, there was another family, what also happened to account for eight, eight people.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because it was the Shamas, the Shamas from shul.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I can't think of his name or anything, but it was the Shamas from shul, with his wife and his kids.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were eight people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that night-- we did not leave that particular night, but we left like a week later.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He talked to me and he came there and says, you can come to my-- to my barn.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That night that we left, they picked up the other family and they shot them all.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were [? not then known. ?] And that was a big plus for us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because there happened to be exactly eight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they knew, after the liquidation of the ghetto, how many people we are.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They figured out who is with us and who was missing, they did-- they did not liquidate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So the word got around that we were killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They keeped--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They kept track who was alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they knew when the German-- when the Germans came in, certain amount of people went to Russia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They did not stay.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so they knew who went there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they knew who wasn't killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they kept watch who was-- who was not killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they thought that we were killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because knowing my father, being a little prominent, so they were looking for him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now they all knew exactly when we were killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went to that guy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we only stayed there two weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
